This is a 41 minute workout called '40 MIN KILLER HIIT WORKOUT - Full Body, No Equipment, Circuit Training - (HIIT IT HARDER DAY 5)' from the channel growingannanas.

It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Adrenaline Rush vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.
